1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:05,000
Welcome to the release presentation of VoltAudit AI.

2
00:00:05,000 --> 00:00:10,000
VoltAudit AI is an enterprise-grade utility bill auditing platform

3
00:00:10,000 --> 00:00:15,000
designed to identify pricing discrepancies and prevent payment losses.

4
00:00:15,000 --> 00:00:20,000
Utility invoices in enterprise environments are highly complex and prone to errors.

5
00:00:20,000 --> 00:00:27,000
Discrepancies in rates, peak hours, and duplicate billings lead to millions in losses.

6
00:00:27,000 --> 00:00:32,000
Auditing these manually is slow and prone to oversight.

7
00:00:32,000 --> 00:00:40,000
VoltAudit AI addresses this through a decoupled, multi-layered architecture.

8
00:00:40,000 --> 00:00:45,000
A FastAPI backend processes requests, exposing tools to the frontend.

9
00:00:45,000 --> 00:00:52,000
The data access layer is strictly isolated behind Model Context Protocol stdio interfaces.

10
00:00:52,000 --> 00:01:00,000
This guards the underlying SQLite database from direct external access.

11
00:01:00,000 --> 00:01:05,000
The core reasoning engine is built around Google's Agent Development Kit,

12
00:01:05,000 --> 00:01:10,000
coordinating an active workforce of eight specialized agents.

13
00:01:10,000 --> 00:01:15,000
From ingestion and vendor resolution to duplicate checks,

14
00:01:15,000 --> 00:01:22,000
each worker acts sequentially, communicating through a shared execution context.

15
00:01:22,000 --> 00:01:27,000
Let's see the system in action using the Streamlit dashboard interface.

16
00:01:27,000 --> 00:01:32,000
We submit a clean utility invoice, and progress indicators track each agent.

17
00:01:32,000 --> 00:01:40,000
The system resolves all checks successfully, grading the run with a perfect score.

18
00:01:40,000 --> 00:01:45,000
When a dirty invoice containing math errors is uploaded, the reconciler flags it.

19
00:01:45,000 --> 00:01:52,000
The risk specialist weighs the deviations, immediately triggering a human approval gateway.

20
00:01:52,000 --> 00:02:00,000
Under the Human Review Queue, administrators inspect the flagged discrepancies.

21
00:02:00,000 --> 00:02:05,000
An operator must write a valid justification text parsed by our governance override skill.

22
00:02:05,000 --> 00:02:12,000
Only approved justifications can bypass the hold and update the status.

23
00:02:12,000 --> 00:02:17,000
VoltAudit AI is fully containerized and production-ready.

24
00:02:17,000 --> 00:02:22,000
With pre-commit quality gates, rigorous type-safety, and local load test validation,

25
00:02:22,000 --> 00:02:30,000
the repository ensures zero downtime and absolute stability.

26
00:02:30,000 --> 00:02:35,000
VoltAudit AI combines enterprise multi-agent ADK systems with a secure architecture.

27
00:02:35,000 --> 00:02:40,000
Delivering intelligent utility cost control. Thank you.
